com.pega.pegarules.pub.generator

Class LiteweightPropertyDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pega.pegarules.pub.generator.LiteweightPropertyDefinition

  • public class LiteweightPropertyDefinition
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a condensed version of a property definition. It is currently used by the tag library iterface in an effort to eliminate the need for ClipboardProperty objects
